thread.title: Michael

author: Michael
title: Michael
text: The purchase process was easy (except for the decision as to which tree), the price was super and my tree arrived in great shape. I purchased the 5-6 foot Red Baron peach due to the low freeze requirements. The only thing that was a surprise was the tiny root that wasn't trimmed off, we expect a much larger root ball. However the tree has been planted, and now we have to wait and see how it manages the AZ desert heat.
